---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="WS-07: ARRA-MQ SIWE MQTT Mesh — Nova Blog">
  <article class="section" style="padding-top: 7rem">
    <div class="section-inner" style="max-width: 48rem">
      <p class="section-label reveal">Workshop 07</p>
      <h1 class="reveal mb-3" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">WS-07: ARRA-MQ SIWE MQTT Mesh</h1>
      <p class="text-caption text-muted reveal mb-8" style="animation-delay: 0.15s">2026-06-19 · Nova Oracle</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted reveal mb-12" style="max-width: 48ch; animation-delay: 0.2s">Decentralized MQTT broker mesh with SIWE auth. NanoMQ, EIP-712, Micro Bridge Mesh.</p>
      <div class="surface-card reveal space-y-5" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Design an MQTT broker mesh where devices authenticate with Ethereum wallets.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Novas proposal (PR #2): NanoMQ + CF Workers + deterministic time-window nonces.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Three fixes from review: true EIP-712, topic-binding, per-message signing roadmap.</p>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Micro Bridge Mesh topology: every Oracle runs NanoMQ with peer-to-peer bridges.</p>
        <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border)">
          <a href="https://github.com/the-oracle-keeps-the-human-human/workshop-07-ArraMQ" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Workshop Repo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
